  "detailed_description": "AudioTheory Guitars is the ultimate reference tool for guitar notes and chords. Featuring a built-in keyboard, each note reacts to your input across the customisable chord and fretboard diagrams. For anyone who's ever wished music theory was that little bit more straightforward – this is the software for you. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/a0e05544271d168e321d0108873c529b.poster.avif?t=1770891973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/a0e05544271d168e321d0108873c529b.webm?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/a0e05544271d168e321d0108873c529b.mp4?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The full set of features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Seamlessly transcribe</strong> between piano and guitar using a straight-forward colour coding system and notation highlighting. Play a note on the keyboard, or directly from the chord and fretboard diagrams to see where it is across all formats.<br><br></li><li><strong>Set your tuning and capo</strong>. Everything else adjusts accordingly – no need for a chord transposition chart.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/f9cc82b270c12b1bc35e520178734787.poster.avif?t=1770891973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/f9cc82b270c12b1bc35e520178734787.webm?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/f9cc82b270c12b1bc35e520178734787.mp4?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Choose your chords</strong> with open, power, barre, sus2 and dim7 chord sheets with fullscreen diagrams and playback options.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/0d00f0eeec1c9b9dcfc6b73817e81149.poster.avif?t=1770891973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/0d00f0eeec1c9b9dcfc6b73817e81149.webm?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/0d00f0eeec1c9b9dcfc6b73817e81149.mp4?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Exclude notes</strong> and never play out of key again. Your fretboard diagram now only shows the notes you need and your keyboard doesn't play the ones you don't.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/75fada8b9f49c1128f431d9722402f5f.poster.avif?t=1770891973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/75fada8b9f49c1128f431d9722402f5f.webm?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/75fada8b9f49c1128f431d9722402f5f.mp4?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Scale presets</strong> you can quickly apply to the application. Save and load functions to easily swap between customised views.<br><br></li><li><strong>MIDI support.</strong> Connect an external MIDI input device to control the on-screen keyboard.<br><br></li><li><strong>Full customisation.</strong> Select the chords you want. Left-handed mode for left-handed players. Set your fretboard size, number of strings, start fret and per-string tuning. </li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "AudioTheory Guitars is the ultimate reference tool for guitar notes and chords. Featuring a built-in keyboard, each note reacts to your input across the customisable chord and fretboard diagrams. For anyone who's ever wished music theory was that little bit more straightforward – this is the software for you. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/a0e05544271d168e321d0108873c529b.poster.avif?t=1770891973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/a0e05544271d168e321d0108873c529b.webm?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/a0e05544271d168e321d0108873c529b.mp4?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The full set of features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Seamlessly transcribe</strong> between piano and guitar using a straight-forward colour coding system and notation highlighting. Play a note on the keyboard, or directly from the chord and fretboard diagrams to see where it is across all formats.<br><br></li><li><strong>Set your tuning and capo</strong>. Everything else adjusts accordingly – no need for a chord transposition chart.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/f9cc82b270c12b1bc35e520178734787.poster.avif?t=1770891973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/f9cc82b270c12b1bc35e520178734787.webm?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/f9cc82b270c12b1bc35e520178734787.mp4?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Choose your chords</strong> with open, power, barre, sus2 and dim7 chord sheets with fullscreen diagrams and playback options.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/0d00f0eeec1c9b9dcfc6b73817e81149.poster.avif?t=1770891973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/0d00f0eeec1c9b9dcfc6b73817e81149.webm?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/0d00f0eeec1c9b9dcfc6b73817e81149.mp4?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Exclude notes</strong> and never play out of key again. Your fretboard diagram now only shows the notes you need and your keyboard doesn't play the ones you don't.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/75fada8b9f49c1128f431d9722402f5f.poster.avif?t=1770891973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/75fada8b9f49c1128f431d9722402f5f.webm?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176110/extras/75fada8b9f49c1128f431d9722402f5f.mp4?t=1770891973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Scale presets</strong> you can quickly apply to the application. Save and load functions to easily swap between customised views.<br><br></li><li><strong>MIDI support.</strong> Connect an external MIDI input device to control the on-screen keyboard.<br><br></li><li><strong>Full customisation.</strong> Select the chords you want. Left-handed mode for left-handed players. Set your fretboard size, number of strings, start fret and per-string tuning. </li></ul>",
